SENIOR THREE
TERMI
Topic 5:
Respiration
Duration: 36 Periods
General Objectives:
By the end of the topic the learner should be able to:
1. understand the processes by which food is broken down to release energy needed for
chemical processes.
2. understand how organism exchange gases with their respiratory medium.

PERIOD
